cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with language theory and grammatical inference in the context of deep learning. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the performance of different types of recurrent neural networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the representation and learning of long-term dependencies in temporal sequences. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper focuses on the performance of neural networks. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the complexity of formal languages and their relation to deep learning.
